  "text": [
    "They lie",
    "under stars in a field.",
    "They lie under rain in a field.",
    "Under sun.",
    "Some people",
    "are like this as well\u2014",
    "like a painting",
    "hidden beneath another painting.",
    "An unexpected weight",
    "the sign of their ripeness."
  ],
  "title": "Green-Striped Melons",
